THE TWO FUSED MEGA-KERNELS (2 launches/layer vs eager's 18)
  decode_attn_fused : RMSNorm + Q/K/V GEMV + KV-cache append + masked single-q
                      FLASH attention (online softmax, KEYS PARALLELIZED across
                      KW warps/head + flash-merge) + O-proj + residual.
                      6 grid.sync() phase barriers. 45 regs, 1024 B smem.
  decode_ffn_fused  : RMSNorm + gate/up GEMV + SwiGLU + down GEMV + residual.
                      4 grid.sync() phase barriers. 37 regs, 1024 B smem.
  Multi-CTA cooperative grid (cuLaunchCooperativeKernel). Each GEMV's output
  rows striped across ALL grid warps (coalesced warp-coop dots). NOT the R9
  single-CTA single-thread-per-row stub.

